Module com.example._50zo

Enum Class CardEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CardEnum>
com.example._50zo.model.CardEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CardEnum>, Constable
public enum CardEnum extends Enum<CardEnum>
Enumeration representing all possible cards in the "Cincuentazo" (Game50) deck.

Each constant in this enum corresponds to a specific playing card, including all ranks (Ace through King) and suits (Hearts, Spades, Diamonds, Clubs), as well as the face-down card used for hidden or undealt cards.

Each card is associated with an image file path that points to its graphical representation used in the game's UI.
